headline: Eaton Recently Set Record High, Now Completing Cup-With-Handle; Can It Blast Higher?
summary: AI play Eaton rose to a record high in late July.  On Wednesday, the manufacturing leader saw a welcome improvement to its Relative Strength (RS) Rating, with an upgrade from 68 to 73.  The upgraded RS Rating shows that Eaton tops more than 70% of all stocks for price performance this past year.
